id: pm-2tan
title: "Plan positional-action help is undiscoverable: pm plan create --help is rejected as an unknown command"
description: Make the documented plan action grammar self-describing so agents can inspect exact create and step flags without falling into generic unknown-command recovery.
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 2
tags[5]: agent-ux,"area:cli",contracts,help,plan
