estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: "pm plan create --help and --help --json resolve to action-specific help or an equally precise positional-action help view; pm help plan create and command-scoped contracts expose the same effective flags; shell completion advertises plan actions; pm plan --help no longer reports an empty subcommands array while describing subcommands only in a positional argument; documented pm plan create examples remain valid; regression tests cover help JSON, contracts, completion, and unknown-command recovery"
