body: "Live reproduction on pm 2026.7.15: pm plan create --help --json exits 2 with unknown_command and says the plan create path is not exposed. The same runtime documents create in the positional subcommand argument of pm plan --help while returning subcommands as an empty array. This violates the repository rule that agents should inspect exact runtime help before mutation. Fix the model coherently: either register real nested subcommands or teach help, contracts, and completion that positional plan actions are command paths. Preserve all plan features and aliases."
